caption.title: Related to Fig 8. Flavivirus NS1-WT but not the NS1-N207Q mutant increase the permeability of HBMEC monolayers.
caption.p: Transendothelial electrical resistance (TEER) assays were used to determine the effect of the WNV and ZIKV NS1-N207Q mutant on NS1-induced hyperpermeability. TEER data here are the non-normalized raw data from Fig 8 displayed in Ohms (Î©). (A) Values from HBMEC treated with WNV NS1 from Fig 8B. (B) Values from HBMEC treated with ZIKV NS1 from Fig 8C.
